Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.18,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{and found us an amazing and \Ntotally extroverted guitarist!}và tìm thấy một tay ghita hướng ngoại rất tuyệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.64,Default,Extroverted Guitarist,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Yế!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.10,Default,Extroverted Guitarist,0,0,0,,Rock you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.27,Default,Kita/Nijika/Ryo,0,0,0,,Yeah! Rock you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.59,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Why couldn't I just accept my mom's help?!}Sao mình không nghe lời mẹ hả trời?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:31.24,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A p-person's collapsed.}C-Có người bất tỉnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.42,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-What do I do? I've got to say something...}L-Làm sao đây? P-Phải nói gì đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:35.92,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Actually, I need an ambulance!}Không, gọi cứu thương.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:38.41,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{H-Hello?}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.90,DefaultItalics,Smartphone,0,0,0,,{This is the news for 4:30 pm...}Tin tức lúc 4:30 phút chiều...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.38,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{W-Water... Please...}N-Nước...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.20,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right! I'll go buy some—}À vâng! Để em đi mua--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.08,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{A-And hangover medicine.}V-Và thuốc chống nôn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:50.92,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right!}V-Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.68,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{And miso soup with clams...}Súp miso với nghêu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.52,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{And rice porridge too...}Và cháo nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:05:00.39,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Preferably in a bed dressed with \Nfreshly line-dried sheets...}Và được nằm trên giường với khăn trải giường mới...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:02.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Sh-She's very demanding.}P-Phiền phức vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.38,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked dark, cramped spaces,}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.75,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{so I'd bury my face deep in my hood}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.13,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{My eyes resented the heartless world,}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.88,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{but yearned for love}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:33.52,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked being soaked by the rain,}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.89,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{because my face looked better clouded over}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:38.53,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I pretended to be afraid of the storm}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.36,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{while waiting for the sky to burst}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:48.32,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum through the light's distortion}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:52.74,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to make thunder roar}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:58.54,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum beyond the pain}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:02.67,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:08.73,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum in a harmonizing quartet}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:12.72,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to cause a revolution}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:18.73,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum in a lamenting forte}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:23.48,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild}
