Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.12,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,222)\fs30\fnTimes New Roman\3c&HAA59B6&\bord2\pos(163.851,160.442)}{Clam\N}{\fs14\c&HAA59B6&\3c&HDFE5E1&\bord1.5}{With the ornithine of 96 clams}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.83,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Ah, right to the liver!}Ấm tới gan luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.35,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{You're a lifesaver! Thanks so much!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:46.70,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I didn't think you'd really \Nbuy me the miso soup!}Không ngờ em lại mua cho chị súp miso đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.82,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-It's nothing.}K-Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.01,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I wanna take off my head and power-wash it!}Muốn tháo đầu ra xong rửa quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.26,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I ended up helping a very weird person.}Mình tự nhiên đi giúp một người kì lạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.13,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I wanna take out my guts \Nand wring out all the alcohol!}Muốn lấy dạ dày ra xong vắt quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.62,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{W-Well, I should be going...}E-Em đi đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.50,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Say, what's your name?}Em tên gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:04.82,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{H-Hitori Gotoh.}Gotoh Hitori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.88,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{What a cute name!}Dễ thương ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.81,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you.}C-Cảm ơn ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.49,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Drinking should be done \Nin moderation, y'know?}Nhậu nhẹt nên điều độ thì tốt hơn nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.04,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{She said as she started drinking again!}Sau khi nói thì chị lại khô máu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.37,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Hair of the dog that bit ya!}Có chơi có chịu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.25,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{So good!}Ngon quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.25,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(106,1)\an8\fnGeorgia\c&H0B0E0F&\3c&HD0DED0&\bord2\4c&H4847CF&\shad1.5}{Onikoro Sake}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.60,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She's still drinking.}Vẫn uống hả trời.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What should I do? Just leave?}Làm sao đây? Mình về được chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:37.22,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Ya want some too, Hitori-chan?}Em muốn uống không Hitori?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.56,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Sorry it's the cheap stuff.}Hàng rẻ tiền thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.62,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{N-No, thanks...}K-Không ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.74,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Wait, you're underage, right?}Em chưa đủ tuổi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.77,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Hey, you listenin'?}Nè, có nghe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.58,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Yeah, she's way too weird.}Chị ấy là người nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.01,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Why haven't ya said anything?}Sao em không nói gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:51.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I can't tell if she's \Nserious or playing dumb.}Mình không thể biết chị ấy đang nghiêm túc hay giỡn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.07,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Hitori-chan, you're cold as ice!}Hitori, em lạnh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.49,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Like concrete!}Y như cục xi măng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{On the count of three, I book it!}Chuồn là thượng sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.00,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Wh-Whaddya want? \NYa want some booze after all?}E-Em muốn gì? Quả nhiên là uống hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.41,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I sh-should be going...}E-Em xin phép...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.92,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Hey, a guitar!}Ghita!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.41,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Do ya play?}Em chơi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:08.75,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I'm in a band too! Indie, of course.}Chị cũng ở trong ban nhạc đó. Khá là Indie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.42,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Sh-She plays too?!}C-Chị ấy cũng chơi nhạc hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.68,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Hey, can ya play?}Nè chơi thử chị xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm s-s-s-so scared!}S-S-Sợ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I've never talked to a \Ngrown-up rocker before!}Mình chưa từng nói chuyện với người ban nhạc khác...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:20.08,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I d-don't know why, but I bet she'll be mad!}K-Không biết tại sao nhưng chị ấy chắc chắn sẽ bực!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.60,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an4\fad(154,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs14\c&HBECC49&\3c&H899256&\bord1\pos(491,50)}{Lemme see\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hLemme see}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.71,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Lemme see! Lemme see!}Cho chị xem nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.86,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Sheesh, kids these days...}Lũ trẻ ngày này...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.61,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{You don't know what rock is!}Em dám xem thường rock hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I have to get out of here \Nbefore I say something stupid.}Phải nói gì đó ngu ngốc rồi chuồn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:33.27,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{What's with you, Hitori-chan?}Sao thế, Hitori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.44,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A-A-A-Actually I bought it \Nbut gave up after one day,}T-T-Thực ra em mua nó nhưng từ bỏ sau 1 ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.53,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{so I was just heading \Nto a pawn shop to sell it!}Nên giờ đang đến cửa hàng để bán nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:39.16,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Uh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.61,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I was hoping for a far more worthy \Nperson to use this guitar}Em hi vọng ai đó tốt hơn mình sẽ chơi nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.75,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{and truly find their wings and soar, \Nbut I d-d-don't play at all!}Tìm thấy nó như chắp thêm đôi cánh để \Nbay cao hơn, chứ em không chơi đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.27,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Sorry! Gosh, wonder how much I'll get for it!}Em xin lỗi! Thật tiếc khi bỏ quá nhiều tiền mua nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:49.79,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's all-you-can-eat yakiniku for me today!}Hôm nay đi ăn yakiniku thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:49.79,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Wait!}Khoan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:55.01,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Giving up after one day is a waste.}Từ bỏ sau 1 ngày thì phí lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.64,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{You can sell it any time you want.}Em có thể bán bất cứ lúc nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.20,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{But if you stick with it \Na little while longer,}Nhưng nếu ráng thêm chút nữa,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.30,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{you might become worthy \Nof that guitar someday.}biết đâu em có thể thích nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:09.52,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, listen to me! Tryin' to sound all wise...}Đùa thôi! Tự nhiên chị lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:09.52,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wait. Is she kind of normal after all?}Ủa? Chị ta tốt bụng vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.35,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, I know.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:14.64,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{How's about I give you lessons?}Để chị dạy em một bài nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.36,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, actually, sorry...}Thực ra... em xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.74,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I lied about everything I said just now.}Lúc nãy là em nói dối...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.54,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{That's a heck of a smooth lie you told.}Nói dối mà trơn tru vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.43,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Wow, nice guitar!}Ghita đẹp đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.16,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{It's clear you take good care of it.}Em bảo dưỡng kĩ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.21,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.45,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I play bass.}Chị chơi Bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:38.18,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Booze and the bass are \Nworth more to me than my life,}Rượu và bass là 2 thứ quan trọng hơn mạng sống của chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.60,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{so I always keep them close by.}Nên luôn giữ chúng bên cạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.39,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{So, uh...}Vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.29,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Where's your bass?}Bass của chị đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.65,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\c&H61ABDA&\frz350.3\move(560.07,66.46,569.68,68.87,23,607)}{Tee hee hee}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.65,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I left it at the pub.}Để ở quán rượu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.86,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Let's go grab it, Hitori-chan!}Đi lấy thôi, Hitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She values her life so little...}Mạng sống của chị ấy... hời hợt quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:00.75,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Hey, hey.}Nè nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.10,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Have you heard back from Bocchi-chan?}Bocchi-chan trả lời chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.20,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Still left on read.}Đã đọc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:09.06,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Maybe we shouldn't have \Nsent those LOINEs.}Đáng ra không nên gửi tin nhắn đó nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:11.00,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I don't think that's it.}Em không nghĩ thế đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.00,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Today's our practice day.}Hôm nay là ngày luyện tập.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.62,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I'm sure she's just busy.}Cậu ấy chỉ bận rộn chút thôi.
