Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.29,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{so there's lots of people around.}nên đông người lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.68,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Perfect for a street performance!}Quá phù hợp để biểu diễn còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:47.67,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, but we don't have amps and stuff...}Cơ mà không có amply nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.68,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{T-Too bad! Guess we'll have \Nto try another time...}Tiếc ghê, vậy để lần sau...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.78,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{H-Hey, it's me!}Tớ nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.47,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I'm not dead!}Vẫn còn sống!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:57.89,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I was gonna play on the street, \Nso could you bring the stuff by for that?}Tớ định diễn trên phố, cậu mang đồ đến được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.47,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Nah, the equipment's enough.}Thiết bị thôi đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:02.15,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-What do I do? She's really going for it...}S-Sao giờ? Chị ấy chơi thật hả...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.12,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:02.15,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Sure, thanks!}Cảm ơn!
