Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.03,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Hey, everyone!}Xin chào mọi người!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.42,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{We're about to play!}Chúng tôi sẽ biểu diễn ngay tại đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:13.20,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{It's free, so come by if you can!}Tất cả đều miễn phí, hãy đến nghe nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.04,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Hey, Kanazawa-Hakkei peeps!}Mọi người ở Kanazawa Hakkei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.35,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{We're about to play!}Chúng tôi sẽ diễn ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.09,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Come watch!}Xin hãy đến xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.32,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wow!}A!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.02,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I can't wait!}Mong chờ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.24,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{You're playing, girl!}Em là người chơi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.63,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Huh? You've never played outside before?}Hả? Em chưa từng chơi bên ngoài bao giờ?\
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.76,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{If you're that scared, \Nyou could shut your eyes...}Nếu sợ vậy thì nhắm mắt vào đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.46,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Or... Well, I guess you're \Nscared of strangers, huh?}Đùa thôi... vậy là em sợ người lạ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.31,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, that might just work...}A, có khi được...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.31,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I feel you.}Chị hiểu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:42.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I've been playing so long in the dark\Nwhere I can't see my fingers anyway.}Lúc nào mình cũng chơi trong bóng tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I can do it.}Ừm, được hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.38,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{But just so you know...}Nhưng chị nói trước...
