Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:12.39,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,Cảm giác không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.94,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Great work, Hitori-chan!}Làm tốt lắm Hitori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:19.13,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you.}C-Cảm ơn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.74,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-What a relief...}M-May quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She didn't realize I only had one eye open!}Chị ấy không biết mình chỉ mở 1 mắt.
