Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.72,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, n-nothing...}K-Không có gì ạ....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:31.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Sorry. I can't change everything all at once!}Xin lỗi chị, em chưa thể hoàn toàn sửa hết điểm yếu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.04,Default,Fan 2,0,0,0,,{Excuse me.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.46,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes?!}V-Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:37.84,Default,Fan 2,0,0,0,,{Can we buy tickets to this concert?}Bọn tớ mua vé được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.16,Default,Fan 1,0,0,0,,{We'll take two!}Cho 2 vé nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.45,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Isn't that great, Hitori-chan?}Tuyệt quá, Hitori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:45.78,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Huh? Did you freeze up from joy?}Ủa? Vui quá đông đá hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:51.06,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Um... That'll be 1,500 yen apiece, 3,000 total!}1 vé 1500, 2 vé 3000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.22,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Right?}Nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:53.31,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,V-Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:57.39,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A-Are you sure you want \Nto buy those t-t-tickets?}H-Hai cậu chắc chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:59.48,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Give it up already, Hitori-chan!}Thôi nào, Hitori. Em phiền quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.36,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-But I...}N-Nhưng em...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.74,Default,Fan 2,0,0,0,,{This was my first time watching a \Nstreet performance, but you were so good!}Lần đầu tớ xem trình diễn đó, nó tuyệt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.81,Default,Fan 1,0,0,0,,{Keep up the good work at \Nyour next concert, okay?}Lần tới hãy cố gắng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.80,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right... I'll do my best.}V-Vâng... tớ sẽ cố gắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.94,Default,Fan 2,0,0,0,,{Will you be playing that song again?}Cậu có chơi lại bài đó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:18.46,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1D1919&\pos(203.5,101.5)\3c&HACA2A6&\bord2}{Onikoro}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.59,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes. I will.}C-Có.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.18,Default,Fan 1,0,0,0,,{Can't wait to see it!}Mong chờ quá đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:23.04,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{To think I had this shining \Nperiod myself once...}Bản thân mình cũng từng trải qua điều này...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.76,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Tonight, I drown away my cares.}Đêm nay phải nhậu quên sầu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.25,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why are you crying?}S-Sao chị lại khóc?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.39,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Sorry, sorry!}Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:32.10,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I'll be back in my happiness spiral soon...}Chị đang quay lại vòng luân hồi hạnh phúc...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.94,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-That can't possibly be good for you.}C-Chắc chắn sau đó sẽ là bể khổ đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:39.20,Default,Cop,0,0,0,,{Excuse me. You guys can't play here!}Xin lỗi, ở đây không được diễn đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.61,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Sorry!}Xin lỗi ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.61,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-It's the fuzz!}C-Cảnh sát!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:42.63,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Are they gonna take me away?!}Mình sẽ bị bắt sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.52,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Of course not!}Ai bắt em đâu mà lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:48.49,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{They }{\i1}{are}{\i0}{ pretty mad, though, \Nso let's call it quits here.}Cơ mà họ không thích đâu nên thôi.\
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,A, phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:59.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I got so carried away before, but I \Nstill have one ticket left to sell...}Tuy đã bán xong nhưng vẫn còn 1 vé...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-But I did sell four!}N-Nhưng bán được 4 tấm rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Not bad for my first time!}Cũng không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.98,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I'll buy that last one.}Chị sẽ mua vé cuối.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.09,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{The ticket.}Vé ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.70,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{That'll get you to your quota, right?}Chỉ tiêu của em mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.35,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-You're sure?!}C-Chị chắc chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:17.47,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Of course. I typically operate \Nout of Shinjuku, so I'm close by,}Dĩ nhiên, chị hay hoạt động ở Shinjuku nên cũng gần.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.40,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{and I know this club too.}Với cả cũng biết Club này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.61,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you so much...}C-Cảm on chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.97,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{A concert costing over five Onikoros...}Một buổi hoà nhạc tiêu tốn hơn 5 Onikoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.26,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{It'd better be worth it!}Chị mong chờ lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.41,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right!}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.97,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Let's play together again some time!}Lần sau chơi cùng nhau nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.75,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Bye-bye, Hitori-chan!}Tạm biệt, Hitori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.09,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{What a mysterious person.}Một người thật kì lạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:43.01,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Rockers really are...}Những tay chơi nhạc...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.18,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{cool.}ngầu ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.76,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I spent the last of my money on your ticket!}Chị xài hết tiền mua vé rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:54.07,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Can I borrow some for the train?}Mượn ít đi tàu được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:57.98,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{I'll pay you back at the concert.}Chị sẽ trả lại ở buổi diễn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:57.98,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{This feels strangely familiar.}Cảm giác hoài niệm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:58.92,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Achoo!}Hắt xi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Why are rockers all so poor?}Sao mấy người chơi nhạc nghèo vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:12.87,Default,Fan 1/Fan 2/Crowd,0,0,0,,{Wow!}Đẹp ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:23.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry I didn't make it to practice today.}Xin lỗi vì đã không đến buổi tập luyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:24.92,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Also...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I sold all my tickets!}Em đã bán hết vé.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.79,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{And... send!}Gửi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:35.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,Cầu cho buổi diễn thành công.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:43.29,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{"Also, I sold all \Nmy tickets," she said!}Cậu ấy nói bán hết vé kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.18,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Bocchi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:47.10,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{She's totally lying, right?}Nói xạo nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:47.95,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Totally.}Chắc chắn luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:52.87,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I bet our LOINEs really \Ndid put pressure on her.}Quả nhiên chúng ta không nên gây áp lực...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.10,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Poor thing.}Tội nghiệp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:58.71,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Let's all be nice to her \Nat practice tomorrow!}Ngày mai hãy nhẹ nhàng với em ấy thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:21:59.55,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:21:59.55,DefaultTop,Kita,0,0,0,,{Right!}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:21.42,Songs_ED2,,0,0,0,,{I sleep, with big problems \Nweighing down on me}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:32.08,Songs_ED2,,0,0,0,,{Though you can't beat that feeling \Nof being loved, it's true}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:41.76,Songs_ED2,,0,0,0,,{When I awaken from cold dreams, \Nmy body feels numb}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:50.50,Songs_ED2,,0,0,0,,{You shine so brightly, \Nit could make me a shadow}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:55.38,Songs_ED2b,,0,0,0,,{It's time to take that step}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:23:03.10,Songs_ED2b,,0,0,0,,{Though there's nothing certain about it}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:10.23,Songs_ED2b,,0,0,0,,{It carries my childish heart into tomorrow}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:14.60,Songs_ED2b,,0,0,0,,{It's time to blast out the thoughts \Nrattling around in my brain}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:17.18,Songs_ED2b,,0,0,0,,{And live, to its fullest, a life}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:22.16,Songs_ED2b,,0,0,0,,{I've been taking advances on for so long}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:24.67,Songs_ED2b,,0,0,0,,{But I also love the days I spend \Nlying around, doing nothing}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.29,Songs_ED2b,,0,0,0,,{So I know I'm going to go see you}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:33.09,Songs_ED2b,,0,0,0,,{Before it all disappears some day}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(3572,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H41403D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\bord2\shad2\4c&H8A51D9&\pos(309,49.5)}#07  To Your House
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:39.78,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Wash'it!}
